{"tid":1692302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學自衛術人數急升　教練稱警方收集資料如白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-11-04T04:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T04:43:52.000Z","uid":152476,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d91986aa4f4fc55721889c24c9e815ed014f54cc","tid":1692302,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有拳館負責人表示，發生721元朗西鐵站襲擊事件後，報讀自衛術的人數較以往多3至4倍。<br />\n<br />\n有學員承認，擔心警察不能保障自己和家人安全，為免受襲擊決定學自衛術。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有拳館教練表示，得悉警方正擬收集教自衛術教練的資料，自己亦在名單之上，認為事件如同白色恐怖，擔心被警方針對，已暫停授課。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489961-20191104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489961-20191104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfjcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=2be4a3a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489961-20191104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b009ecc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489961-20191104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"91366fc883d540763b70323af3e64ffb3cfd5199","tid":1692302,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"以為講緊示威者學<br />\n乜佢地上堂無學過咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac18929ab681834f4afe754c986df41c128b83d","tid":1692302,"uid":25424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"政治部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年有印刷機要同政治部拎牌<br />\n<br />\n驚人同左仔印傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63d119122aed0c98f6df2b692e8cb9d58904d6c","tid":1692302,"uid":256142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:25:02.000Z